A box with dog poo in it showed up at my front door the second I hit the download button. On it was a note that said â€œThanks for downloading my app, idiot. I love u - Donald TrumpğŸ’‹â€ with the official White House seal. When I actually got into the app it kept crashing and/or taking me to YouTube videos from 2014. Now my phone wonâ€™t stop playing Thrift Shop by Macklemore. I literally canâ€™t get it to stop. Macklemoreâ€™s hit song â€œThrift Shopâ€ is blaring throughout my house constantly, as my phone has somehow become connected to every one of my speakers. The song, which describes a trip taken by musical artist Macklemore to an open-air market in Seattle, has now been playing on a loop for a solid 2 hours and 7 minutes. The hit single is on a volume so high that every window in my house broke. Does anyone know how to fix this????
